{"tid":1228692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】向公務員事務局投訴警犬template！","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T18:11:38.000Z","uid":235080,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2556f4826363e16b4dbd1d501fec7f5a39353400","tid":1228692,"uid":235080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:45:32.000Z","msg":"面對烈士犧牲 暫緩修例 警犬濫權<br />\n香港人要學識嘅係自己救自己<br />\n聽日遊行 如果你見到<span style=\"color: red;\">警犬作出不恰當行為</span><br />\n請你用<span style=\"color: red;\">下面template</span>向<span style=\"color: red;\">公務員事務局</span>投訴<br />\n<br />\n<strong>------------------------------</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中文版template:</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色字</span>表示要修改嘅字眼<br />\n<br />\n曾先生：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>投訴<span style=\"color: green;\">俞頌豪警員</span>於2019年6月16日的表現</strong><br />\n<br />\n本人對<span style=\"color: green;\">俞頌豪警員</span> (編號<span style=\"color: green;\">77769</span>) 於2019年6月16日的表現甚感不滿，特此來函作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n該警員<span style=\"color: green;\">在無預先警告下開槍</span>，令人失望。<br />\n<br />\n對此，本人希望有關部門能作出跟進。謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n〇〇祝<br />\n工作順利<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">張添添</span> 啟<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月16日<br />\n<br />\n<strong>------------------------------</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文版template:</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色字</span>表示要修改嘅字眼<br />\n<br />\nDear Mr. Tsang,<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Complaint against the behaviour of officer <span style=\"color: green;\">Yu Chung Ho</span> on 16th June 2019</strong><br />\n<br />\nI am writing to lodge a complaint against the misbehaviour of officer <span style=\"color: green;\">Yu Chung Ho</span> (No. <span style=\"color: green;\">77769</span>) on 16th June 2019.<br />\n<br />\nIt was disappointing that the officer has <span style=\"color: green;\">fired without giving a warning in advance</span>.<br />\n<br />\nWe seek your help in urging relevant departments to follow up. Thank you!<br />\n<br />\nYours sincerely,<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">Daniel Cheung</span><br />\n<br />\n16th June 2019<br />\n<br />\n<strong>------------------------------</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>記住要<span style=\"color: red;\">fax加email</span>:</strong><br />\nFax: 2868 5069<br />\nEmail: csbcomp@csb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KeKNgDW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeKNgDW.png&h=1f178f5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1B3m5xC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1B3m5xC.png&h=596fef90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"274d3236c9cd523bf8d3ef676996e1214eebcf75","tid":1228692,"uid":235080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:48:19.000Z","msg":"請大家幫手push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e6e987a67946bdbcadea236b315b03ed38c3cd","tid":1228692,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:49:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"41a1d41790d9e29b542728709c86c44542120aae","tid":1228692,"uid":257330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:53:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0bb6133ed754ba8fd25088f07ec677fba2c00bb8","tid":1228692,"uid":194108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5544ccce51a113023d561efca3dd7f25b1e8aa41","tid":1228692,"uid":219128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5b9a3842f1960ff48370074edc5038f038a1cc59","tid":1228692,"uid":62776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:00:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n為左令過往既犧牲唔好白廢<br />\n呢d野係應該要做既"},{"pid":"b47e6b149b6f90b82570f5317ec90ff040dc3ed5","tid":1228692,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:42:00.000Z","msg":