PO.  CSB, just like other government bureaux/ departments, is not authorised to handle the complaints against the Police under the existing mechanism and the relevant ordinance.  <br />\n<br />\nAs for your views in your email of 19 June 2019, we have also relayed  to CAPO for their consideration."},{"pid":"8b6c2d3bdd01cab271e74561baca8dbe72795ac9","tid":1228692,"uid":169646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T20:55:28.000Z","msg":"雖然唔知成效大唔大, 但係照Push"},{"pid":"ac0187b3a95e9dcf39cff227200f82146e0b0706","tid":1228692,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"8ca467c2aa8480b89463d4897dfb2141e629347f","tid":1228692,"uid":235080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:46:58.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"78766b79739b4bee5eede66a602c2be4f7ab202e","tid":1228692,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}